nodes.text: Darth Vader 7 is the seventh issue of the canon comic series Star Wars: Darth Vader. It was written by Greg Pak, illustrated by Raffaele Ienco, and published by Marvel Comics on November 11, 2020.
The issue features the story "Into the Fire Part II: The Assassin," in which Darth Vader struggles to survive the embers of Mustafar, as he faces Ochi of Bestoon, assassin of the Sith.
